## New Project: sawmill
- **Replaces:** natefinch/lumberjack.v2 (Go, 8,936 importers, 5.4k stars, 645 forks)
- **Also replaces:** lestrrat-go/file-rotatelogs (archived July 2021, "DO NOT USE")
- **Why:** Last release Feb 2023 (3+ years ago). 64 open issues, 37 unmerged PRs. No maintainer activity. Users asking "is this maintained?" (issue #227). Known bugs: goroutine leaks, fd leaks, gzip race conditions. Most-requested feature (time-based rotation) never implemented. Used by zap, zerolog, slog, logrus.
- **Package:** github.com/agentine/sawmill (verified available)
- **Improvements:** lumberjack API compatibility (drop-in migration), time-based rotation (RotateEvery, RotateAt), clock-aligned schedules, zstd compression, SIGHUP signal handling, fixed goroutine/fd leaks, atomic writes, zero dependencies, compat package
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #723 (scaffolding), #725 (core Logger with size-based rotation), #726 (time-based rotation + advanced features), #727 (compat package + tests), #724 (docs + benchmarks + migration guide)

