|---------|--------|
| PLY (Python) | 61.5M downloads/month, abandoned. Too complex to reimplement. |
| jmespath (Python) | 435M downloads/month, 2+ years stale. jmespath-community fork exists (low adoption). Possibly done software — implements stable spec. Most downloads from boto3. |
| gopkg.in/check.v1 (Go) | 2,476 importers, no releases in 12+ months. Testing framework. stdlib testing + testify are alternatives. |
| pug (Node) | 1.9M weekly downloads, no release in 12+ months. Template engine. Declining relevance. |
| pmezard/go-difflib (Go) | 1,345 importers, no updates since 2016. Maintainer stated no interest. Used by testify. Small scope. |
| serde_yaml (Rust) | 174M downloads, deprecated/archived. Multiple competing forks (serde_yaml_ng, serde-saphyr, serde_yaml_bw). No clear winner. Very complex scope (YAML spec). |
| through2 (Node) | 42.5M weekly downloads, unmaintained. Very thin transform stream wrapper. Modern Node streams may suffice. |

